[05/01/2018 02:35:09] <font color="#ffffff">Exacto.</font>
[05/01/2018 02:35:12] <font color="#ffff00">Un vecindario discreto</font>
[05/01/2018 02:35:12] <font color="#ffff00">y una sencilla decoración,</font>
