[05/01/2018 19:22:38] <font color="#ffff00">de estrella Michelin</font>
[05/01/2018 19:22:40] <font color="#ffff00">con un precio</font>
[05/01/2018 19:22:40] <font color="#ffff00">y unas vistas de altura,</font>
