[05/01/2018 23:16:47] <font color="#ffff00">(R E)</font>
[05/01/2018 23:16:53] <font color="#0000ff">(Música)</font>
[05/01/2018 23:17:35] <font color="#0000ff">(Piano)</font>
[05/01/2018 23:18:48] <font color="#ffff00">¡Ay, frijoles!</font>
[05/01/2018 23:18:48] <font color="#ffffff">Come, mi niña, come.</font>
